# PrayerMap Project Overview

## Identity
PrayerMap is a location-based spiritual platform enabling users to share prayer requests and support one another through a beautifully designed map interface.

**Mission:** "See where prayer is needed. Send prayer where you are."
**Live Site:** https://prayermap.net
**Status:** 100% non-profit ministry

## The Living Map Principle (ABSOLUTE PRIORITY)
PrayerMap is the world's first LIVING MAP where users witness prayer in real-time and see eternal memorial connections.

**Non-Negotiable Requirements:**
- Real-time updates <2 seconds
- Memorial lines are ETERNAL (never expire, never delete)
- Universal shared map (everyone sees same prayer history)
- Live witnessing experience is THE product

## Tech Stack
- **Frontend:** React 18 + TypeScript + Vite
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui + Framer Motion
- **Maps:** Mapbox GL JS
- **State:** TanStack Query (React Query)
- **Backend:** Supabase (PostgreSQL + Auth + Realtime + Edge Functions)
- **Deployment:** Vercel (web) + Capacitor (iOS/Android)

